spirit:component.spirit:description: This core provides division using one of three algorithms. The LUT-Mult algorithm is suitable for very small operands. The Radix-2 algorithm provides a solution suitable for small to medium operand division, and High Radix algorithm provides a solution based upon XtremeDSP slices and so is well suited to larger operands (that is, above about 16 bits wide).
